YAML configuration language
    used in devops tools like ansible, docker, kubernetes

we write dockercompose file in yaml
we write kubernetes manifest file in yaml
 we write ansible list in yaml


The entire yaml file is of key value pair type


characteristics of YAML
  YAML aint a markup language

  its used for data serialization like xml, json but not a substitute

  helps in exchange between people and computer 
  All programming languages have library for YAML 
  It can be used in arrays and dictionaries
  extension can be .yml, .yaml


Data serialization
  Process of converting a data that could be stored or sent over a network
  we can use python to serialize the data and send it over to another program...where we can
use javascript to deserialize and use it
